# M6 smoothness verification — walks left/right + jets to expose any
# remaining mech-vs-world jitter after the camera-follow fix.
#
# The renderer reads `update_camera`'s SHOT_LOG line every tick — grep
# for "cam t=" in the .log to see:
#   - raw_pel.y       : post-physics pelvis (what the OLD code followed)
#   - lerp_pel.y      : the lerped pelvis (what the renderer draws)
#   - L_foot/R_foot   : the per-tick foot Y (oscillate with the gait)
#   - focus.y         : what update_camera now feeds smooth-follow
#                       (grounded RUN/STAND → stable; airborne → lerp_pel)
#   - cam_prev.y      : last frame's camera target Y
#   - grounded / anim : context
#
# Expect: focus.y stable while running on flat ground, even as L/R_foot
# alternate between planted (chain_below) and lifted (chain_below-9).
# Expect: raw_pel.y still oscillates by ~4.5 px every gait half-cycle.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/m6_smoothness
map    reactor
spawn_at 600 600
aim    900 600

# Settle on the ground.
at  30 shot t030_idle

# Walk right for ~2 seconds (multiple gait cycles).
at  60 press right
at  90 shot t090_walk_a
at 120 shot t120_walk_b
at 150 shot t150_walk_c
at 180 release right

# Settle again.
at 210 shot t210_settled

# Walk left.
at 240 press left
at 270 shot t270_walk_left_a
at 300 shot t300_walk_left_b
at 330 release left

# Settle.
at 360 shot t360_settled

# Jet straight up.
at 390 press jet
at 420 shot t420_jet_up_a
at 450 shot t450_jet_up_b
at 480 release jet

# Descend + land.
at 540 shot t540_landed

# Jet diagonally.
at 570 press right
at 570 press jet
at 600 shot t600_jet_right_a
at 630 shot t630_jet_right_b
at 660 release right
at 660 release jet
at 720 shot t720_after

contact_sheet smoothness_sheet cols 4

at 780 end
